Package domain

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Dictionary
    Represents dictionaries having ByteSequence as key and Integer as value.
    SimpleQueue<E>  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArrayQueue
    SimpleQueue implementation for HuffNode elements that internally uses an array to store them.
    BitSequence
    Represents a sequence of bits of arbitrary length.
    ByteSequence
    Represents a sequence of bytes.
    CompressionAlgorithm
    An abstract class with methods for data compression/decompression.
    Huffman
    A CompressionAlgorithm implementation which uses canonical Huffman coding.
    HuffNode
    Represents a node in a Huffman tree.
    HuffNode.ByCanonicalOrder
    Compares HuffNodes by canonical order: first by codeword length (in ascending order), then by symbol (in alphabetical order).
    HuffNode.ByWeight
    Compares HuffNodes by weight, in ascending order.
    LZW
    A CompressionAlgorithm implementation which uses the Lempel–Ziv–Welch algorithm with variable-length codewords and dictionary resets when full.
    LZWDictEntry
    Represents an LZWDictionary entry.
    LZWDictionary
    A Dictionary implementation which uses internally a hash table with separate chaining with linked lists.
    TreeRepresentation
    Represents a canonical Huffman tree.
    Utils
    A general purpose utility class.
